## Outcome

Successfully transformed AETHER from a basic Windows AD lab into a multi-OS centralized identity environment.

Validated:

- Kerberos authentication
- DNS-based domain service discovery
- Linux AD enrollment
- Samba / Winbind integration
- SMB file sharing across OS boundaries
- Domain group mapping into Linux security model

AETHER now functions as a small organizational domain environment with centralized identity and cross-platform resource access.

---

## Notes

This was one of the most satisfying homelab milestones so far.

Lab now feels less like “a collection of VMs” and more like:

```text
an actual organization
```

where identity and permissions follow the user across systems regardless of operating system.
